[[File:Whiteia.JPG|thumb|right|''[[Whiteia]]'' fossils]]

'''Actinistia''' is a [[Class (biology)|subclass]] of mostly [[fossil]] [[lobe-finned fish]]es.  This subclass contains the [[coelacanth]]s (Order Coelacanthiformes), including the two living species of coelacanths, both of the genus ''[[Latimeria]]'': the [[West Indian Ocean coelacanth]] and the [[Indonesian coelacanth]].

